145
00:09:32.780 --> 00:09:36.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Back home while I was in a band,
I learned it for fun.

146
00:09:36.534 --> 00:09:37.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
From Yasu?

147
00:09:39.120 --> 00:09:40.663 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why do you know about Yasu?

148
00:09:40.746 --> 00:09:44.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Because when Nobu gets drunk,
he always talks about Yasu.

149
00:09:44.458 --> 00:09:47.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Last night too, he kept saying
how he wished that Yasu was here.

150
00:09:48.004 --> 00:09:50.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
