is to sever his relationship with me?

263
00:17:41.977 --> 00:17:43.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Did you sleep with Mizukoshi?

264
00:17:43.395 --> 00:17:45.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-No way!
-You're lying!

265
00:17:45.105 --> 00:17:47.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Why would he give you
that much if you didn’t?

266
00:17:47.524 --> 00:17:48.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It’s not a lie!

267
