268
00:17:50.944 --> 00:17:52.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and will be getting married.

269
00:17:52.279 --> 00:17:54.656 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
